## Content Security Policy

Headers set in `next.config.ts`:
```ts
{
  'Content-Security-Policy': [
    "default-src 'self'",
    "script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://js.stripe.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://consent.cookiebot.com",
    "frame-src https://js.stripe.com",
    "img-src 'self' data: blob: https://*.r2.dev https://lh3.googleusercontent.com",
    "connect-src 'self' https://*.supabase.co https://api.stripe.com https://*.typesense.net wss://*.supabase.co https://app.posthog.com https://eu.posthog.com",
    "style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com",
    "font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com",
  ].join('; ')
}
```
